00:56:16,887 --> 00:56:18,002
<i>Vaya amiga.</i>

889
00:56:18,167 --> 00:56:18,917
Julien.

890
00:56:19,447 --> 00:56:21,005
<i>¿No está estupenda así?</i>

891
00:56:21,167 --> 00:56:22,043
